\n<Male>Hey, hey, it's today, right? The day that "she" comes to
town...!!!
\n<Male>Yeah, it's today. So, what kind of girl will she be?

\n<Male>She's supposed to be quite emotional, right? Looking forward
to it-!

\n<Eury>I am the modified girl, Eury! Now that I'm here, everything
will be alright!
\n<Eury>I will protect the peace of this town!
\n<Eury>Heheh, as expected. Everyone was waiting for me, right?!

\n<Eury>Everyone is looking at me with eyes full of respect...!
Modified girl, the best~!

\n<Eury>Finally, a solo mission entrusted to me! This inn will be my
base, and my story as a modified girl begins now!

\n<Eury>But first, let's go on patrol to see if anyone is in
trouble!
